arch-home
Contact: pyther@pyther.net
Website: http://pyther.net/projects/arch-home/

Description: arch-home is a flask app that generates an Arch Linux homepage.

Features

    * News Headlines
    * Latest Packages
    * Google Search
    * Arch Search (Forums, Wiki, AUR, and Bugs)
    * Testing Packages in Italics

Link:
    http://arch.pyther.net

Dependencies:
    * Python 2.6
    * flask
    * python-feedparser 4.1 - http://www.feedparser.org/


Deploying
  * http://flask.pocoo.org/docs/deploying/


Testing
  python2 index.py


Bugs/Feature Requests:
    Please submit all bugs and feature requests here: http://github.com/pyther/arch-home/issues


Notes:
    *PKG version or revision might be removed to make the pkg fit on one line
    *News and Package lists are fetched every 60 minutes
    *Will not work with IE, because IE does not support mimetype application/xhtml+xml

